feet off the gas.
(horn honking)

200
00:08:01,715 --> 00:08:02,782
I'm on the wheel
and on the gas.

201
00:08:03,783 --> 00:08:05,185
All right, all right.

202
00:08:05,185 --> 00:08:06,419
Wait, wait, don't--
don't let go.
You got the wheel?

203
00:08:06,419 --> 00:08:07,420
No, I don't.

204
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,421
Just one sec.

205
00:08:08,421 --> 00:08:09,422
